graph TB
    subgraph "User Layer"
        User[User Browser]
    end

    subgraph "Production Environment - AWS"
        CF[CloudFront CDN]
        S3[S3 Bucket<br/>Static Assets]
        APIGW[API Gateway]
        Lambda[Lambda Function<br/>FastAPI + Mangum]
        DDB[DynamoDB<br/>Resume Data]
        
        CF -->|Static Files| S3
        CF -->|API Requests| APIGW
        APIGW -->|Invoke| Lambda
        Lambda -->|Read/Write| DDB
    end

    subgraph "Local Development Environment - Docker"
        Nginx[Nginx<br/>Reverse Proxy<br/>:8080]
        FastAPI[FastAPI Container<br/>:8000]
        LocalStack[LocalStack<br/>AWS Services]
        LocalDDB[Local DynamoDB]
        
        Nginx -->|Proxy /api| FastAPI
        Nginx -->|Serve Static| Nginx
        FastAPI -->|AWS SDK| LocalStack
        LocalStack -->|Simulates| LocalDDB
    end

    subgraph "Data Management"
        Excel[Excel Template<br/>Instructions<br/>Profile<br/>WorkExperience<br/>Education<br/>Skills]
        Seed[seed_database.py<br/>Kill & Fill]
        
        Excel -->|Load Data| Seed
        Seed -->|Populate| DDB
        Seed -->|Populate| LocalDDB
    end

    subgraph "Security & Validation"
        reCAPTCHA[Google reCAPTCHA v2]
        RateLimit[Rate Limiting<br/>6 requests/hour<br/>2 hour block]
    end

    subgraph "CI/CD Pipeline - Planned"
        GH[GitHub Repository]
        Actions[GitHub Actions]
        TF[Terraform<br/>Infrastructure as Code]
        
        GH -->|Trigger| Actions
        Actions -->|Deploy| TF
        TF -->|Provision| APIGW
        TF -->|Provision| Lambda
        TF -->|Provision| DDB
        TF -->|Provision| S3
        TF -->|Provision| CF
    end

    subgraph "Testing & Quality"
        PreCommit[Pre-commit Hooks]
        PyTest[pytest Unit Tests]
        
        PreCommit -->|Run| PyTest
    end

    User -->|HTTPS| CF
    User -->|Local Dev| Nginx
    User -->|Submit Contact Form| reCAPTCHA
    reCAPTCHA -->|Verify| Lambda
    RateLimit -->|Protect| Lambda
    
